name: Enonville_Scalloped_3-Drawer_Console_Table
reviews: By looking at the picture it seems well finished. It is not. There are drip marks, brush marks, bubbles everywhere. And not cute character antique-ish looking ones. I mean homemade painted by a five year old paint marks/mistakes. I am sure people will ask me if I painted it myself at some point. Definitely not worth the price.
Love the style and the look. The quality is not as good as I expected, but I am overall very happy with how this piece looks and functions in my dining room.
This came with a few chips that I had to fix myself!! And not very level when put together!!
description:
Add a touch of whimsy to your foyer or living room with this three-drawer console table. Both functional and decorative, this three-drawer console table is a stylish addition to your home. Made of wood with a black and brown finish, the table features three hand-painted drawers for storing small items. The table's scalloped lower shelf and fluted legs bring additional charm to this transitional piece.
